13
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:21,700
♫   An air of melancholy surrounds me as the Bodhi leaves fall   ♫

14
00:01:23,810 --> 00:01:27,879
   

15
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:30,050
   

16
00:01:30,050 --> 00:01:35,900
   

17
00:01:43,060 --> 00:01:47,100
We agreed to frame Yan Dan for a small mistake and chase her out of Yanxu Heavenly Palace.

18
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:48,199
Why did you break your promise?

19
00:01:48,199 --> 00:01:51,379
Are you out of your mind? This is Yuqing Palace!

20
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:57,099
You were the one who gave her the lotus root that harmed her.

21
00:01:57,099 --> 00:01:58,780
Why are you pretending to be innocent?

22
00:01:58,780 --> 00:02:01,280
Now you're telling me to act in good faith?

23
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:04,899
I was just worried that Yan Dan would make a big mistake in the future.

24
00:02:04,899 --> 00:02:06,780
I wanted to lightly punish her so she would realize that.

25
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:08,440
I didn't intend to kill her.

26
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:11,239
She just received the thunder strikes after losing half her heart.

27
00:02:11,239 --> 00:02:13,919
If she is found guilty and sent to the Heavenly Gallows again,

28
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:17,679
even if she survives, she'll revert to her original form!

29
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:22,960
My intention was for her to disappear from this world.

30
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:33,340
Zhi Xi, no matter if the punishment is serious or not, you've already gotten your hands dirty.

31
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:36,140
Your sisterhood ties with her have been severed long ago.

32
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:39,620
This case has alerted His Supreme Majesty.

33
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:43,140
You had better keep quiet if you don't wish

34
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:47,500
to ruin both your career and life.

35
00:03:04,420 --> 00:03:07,980
 Why? Why did everything end up like this? 

36
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:10,600
 What exactly went wrong? 

37
00:03:24,820 --> 00:03:28,219
His Majesty has ordered us to move all these things away in two hours.

38
00:03:28,219 --> 00:03:30,040
No delays are allowed.

39
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:32,950
   

40
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,380
What are you doing?

41
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:55,519
How dare you taint His Majesty's item with your terrible embroidery?

42
00:03:55,519 --> 00:03:58,160
It's no wonder His Majesty couldn't wait any longer.

43
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:04,199
He has ordered his men to move all your wretched belongings out of the palace.

44
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:09,560
 Emperor Ying Yuan, do you hate me that much? 

45
00:04:10,580 --> 00:04:14,460
You should enjoy the view while you can.

46
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:20,120
Now that you've stepped out the palace door, you won't be able to return again.

47
00:04:20,810 --> 00:04:25,339
Looking at you now, I'm reminded of my past self.

48
00:04:25,339 --> 00:04:30,340
However, I left the palace gloriously for a promotion,

49
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:34,200
while you're leaving in shame.

50
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:38,700
No matter if it's me, who was assigned to His Majesty by His Supreme Majesty,

51
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:41,840
or Zhi Xi, who sacrificed half her heart to save his life...

52
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:47,240
No fairy can stay in Yanxu Heavenly Palace forever.

53
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:51,199
His Majesty's heart only has space for the beings of the Three Realms.

54
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:53,500
His heart has no space for a single woman.

55
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,040
Is that so?

56
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:59,800
If that's true, why did you rack your brain just to transfer me from the palace?

57
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:02,780
I wasn't the one who chased you out and sent you to prison.

58
00:05:02,780 --> 00:05:04,680
It was him!

59
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:07,879
So what if he played GO with you and taught you divine arts?

60
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:12,959
To him, you're nothing but an inferior attendant who's there to entertain him.

61
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:20,820
However, you're different from the others indeed.

62
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:26,060
Unlike all the fairies who left the palace, you're leaving in shame.

63
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:29,300
Do you know what His Majesty said about you?

64
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:33,880
He said you were a disgrace to Yanxu Heavenly Palace.

65
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:38,759
He has ordered his men to burn your belongings in the Soul Incinerator.

66
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:47,260
You should have seen this coming, from the day you harbored thoughts...

67
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:50,360
you shouldn't have had.

68
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:53,620
Take her away!

69
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:55,360
 Yes. 

70
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:02,720
   

71
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:45,680
You must have suffered.

72
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:49,240
Why?

73
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:52,560
Why did you do this to me?

74
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,300
I'm sorry.

75
00:06:55,620 --> 00:07:02,680
I just wanted to frame you for a small mistake, so that you could leave Yanxu Heavenly Palace and His Majesty's side.

76
00:07:04,100 --> 00:07:06,900
I don't want you to be trapped by love.

77
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:13,700
I didn't expect Ying Deng to use me as her pawn and land you in this state.

78
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:19,120
I know nothing I say matters now.

79
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:22,500
However, I truly did it for your sake initially—

80
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:24,500
For my sake?

81
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:30,499
If so, why didn't you speak up for me when Ying Deng framed me for the poison?

82
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:35,620
Do you know how you looked back then?

83
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:39,220
I felt like you were no longer the sister I knew.

84
00:07:39,220 --> 00:07:41,740
I was a coward.

85
00:07:41,740 --> 00:07:48,280
I didn't dare to admit my mistake in front of His Supreme Majesty and His Majesty.

86
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:50,520
Ever since I was little...

87
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:57,660
I always thought you were the dearest person to me.

88
00:07:57,660 --> 00:08:02,320
I thought you would always protect and support me.

89
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:07,800
Even if everyone else betrayed me, I've always thought you wouldn't.

90
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:14,620
I even swore a secret vow that I would share joy and sorrow with you.

91
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:16,760
But now...

92
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:20,360
After all that has happened...

93
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:26,679
Now that I'm looking at the current you, I still don't understand what happened.

94
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:32,400
Can you please tell me why you did that?

95
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:40,130
Since we were little, you always thought I was strong and didn't fear anything, right?

96
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:43,570
It was because you didn't understand me at all.

97
00:08:43,570 --> 00:08:47,659
You don't know how much I've suffered all these years!

98
00:08:48,660 --> 00:08:50,420
You suffered?

99
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:56,119
Ever since we acquired our human forms, and after His Majesty said...

100
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:59,860
that I was the weaker twin,

101
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:06,680
I started training harder than anyone I knew

102
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:09,680
so that people would not take me lightly!

103
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:18,440
You understood the essence of the Xiaohan Scriptures just by copying it.

104
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:24,240
Something that's easy for you to attain was actually my lifelong wish.

105
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:27,660
I've never wanted you to be sent to the Mortal Realm for me.

106
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:30,940
However, you requested it in public.

107
00:09:30,940 --> 00:09:33,640
People mocked my ineptitude.

108
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:39,000
I finally became Deputy Curator, yet you went and stole my job.

109
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,960
You eliminated devils and protected His Majesty.

110
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:45,140
Everyone took me lightly.

111
00:09:45,140 --> 00:09:50,360
Even your fellow attendants mocked me behind my back!

112
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:58,540
I didn't expect you...

113
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:05,640
to be troubled over people saying that you were the weaker twin.

114
00:10:07,540 --> 00:10:10,460
I actually didn't notice at all.

115
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:15,980
I know you didn't want to go to the mortal world.

116
00:10:15,980 --> 00:10:18,640
You wanted to be promoted.

117
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:23,219
That's why I wanted to use my own ways to help you out as much as I could.

118
00:10:24,220 --> 00:10:28,220
However, I've never thought about how you felt.

119
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:33,500
I've never asked you about it, causing you to hold a huge grudge against me.

120
00:10:35,380 --> 00:10:37,240
I thought...

121
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:42,040
we could walk together, hand in hand, forever.

122
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:47,060
I thought... we would always be best sisters.

123
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:49,460
But I didn't expect that...

124
00:10:50,580 --> 00:10:54,640
I didn't expect us to end up like this.

125
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:59,320
I'm sorry.

126
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:03,020
I'm a terrible sister.

127
00:11:05,620 --> 00:11:07,680
I'm sorry.

128
00:11:09,300 --> 00:11:11,080
Yan Dan.

129
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:14,580
I'm sorry.

130
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:20,440
I know. This is my fault.

131
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:38,540
I'm sure you've held this grudge for a century.

132
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:42,380
You may never let go of it...

133
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:46,380
as long as I'm around.

134
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:51,060
Maybe now, the best outcome for us...

135
00:11:52,740 --> 00:11:55,460
is to never see each other again.

136
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,600
Zhi Xi.

137
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:05,800
Live well for yourself.

138
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:09,000
Leave now.

139
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:11,200
Yan Dan!

140
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:14,700
Leave!

141
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:22,300
Just go!

142
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:07,000
Your Majesty, although Yan Dan is mischievous, she has a kind nature.

143
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,000
I don't believe that she's the culprit.

144
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:12,800
Should we really do nothing about it as she receives the punishment of fire?

145
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:20,900
Yan Dan isn't willing to speak the truth to protect the person she wants to protect.

146
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:28,800
However, I will not let her suffer for a crime she didn't commit.

147
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:33,200
I will find other evidence and prove her innocence.

148
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:43,600
Your Majesty, this is an immortal attendant from Qianyun Palace.

149
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,800
He's here to look for Yan Dan.

150
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,200
Why are you looking for her?

151
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:54,100
Your Majesty, Fairy Yan Dan told me to burn this agarwood incense burner with fire a few days ago.

152
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:57,800
However, the incense burner is blessed with divine arts. I couldn't burn it, no matter what I did.

153
00:13:57,800 --> 00:14:00,600
I had no choice but to return it to her,

154
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,800
but I couldn't find her.

155
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:16,000
I will return it to her.

156
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:18,000
You all may leave, for now.

157
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:32,800
 Yan Dan, since you were willing to burn this agarwood incense burner,  

158
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:35,100
 I'm sure you are thoroughly disappointed with me. 

159
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:41,000
 However, the only way for you to sever your emotions is to leave Yanxu Heavenly Palace. 

160
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:45,200
 By doing so, you will no longer be hurt or sad in the future. 

161
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:58,000
   

162
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:25,800
  Yu Mo! This is bad. Something huge happened! 

163
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:27,400
Didn't you tell me this yourself?

164
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:30,000
"We shouldn't panic, no matter what." Why are you panicking?

165
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:32,600
  For some reason, Yan Dan was arrested for poisoning the Curator! 

166
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:34,500
  Emperor Ying Yuan had sent her to Heavenly Prison! 

167
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:36,400
  We have to save her! 

168
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:37,800
Don't worry.

169
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:40,900
I will surely try everything to save her.

170
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:58,900
Brother Yu Mo. Brother Yu Mo!

171
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:01,000
Brother Yu Mo!

172
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:07,700
Brother Yu Mo, why are you trying to break the barrier, all of a sudden?

173
00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:10,600
Did you know that Yan Dan was sent to the Heavenly Prison?

174
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:13,700
However, this barrier is connected to my immortal spirit.

175
00:16:13,700 --> 00:16:17,600
Anyone can enter and exit at will, except for me.

176
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,000
This won't do.

177
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:21,600
I have to rescue Yan Dan as soon as possible.

178
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:28,000
Brother Yu Mo! Since Yan Dan is your friend, naturally, she's my friend as well.

179
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,600
I'll find the Marshal right now so that he can dispel the barrier.

180
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,800
Don't do that!

181
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:34,400
Marshal Huo De will never agree to it.

182
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:38,000
It's impossible for me to leave Yan Dan in the lurch.

183
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:42,900
I must save her, even if it means I have to sacrifice myself.

184
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:02,700
Lu Ming?

185
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:07,000
Don't worry about me.

186
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:09,200
I'm doing great over here.

187
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,800
  Do you even know the situation you're in? 

188
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:15,300
  Yan Dan, you have to tell His Majesty the entire truth now. 

189
00:17:15,300 --> 00:17:18,500
  If not, you'll die! 

190
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:24,000
  I'd never believe that you were the culprit behind the poisoning incident. 

191
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:29,100
  Apart from you, Zhi Xi is the only Four-Leaf Lotus in the entire Heavenly Palace! 

192
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:33,200
  Are you keeping quiet because you want to protect her? 

193
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:41,800
  Even though Zhi Xi is your sister, she framed you for her crime. 

194
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:45,200
  I'll go explain everything to His Majesty now if you insist on keeping quiet! 

195
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,900
No!

196
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:52,800
You mustn't do that if you see me as your friend.

197
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:54,400
But why?

198
00:17:55,100 --> 00:17:58,200
I've already discussed it with Zhi Xi.

199
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:00,500
She has her painful reasons.

200
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,700
I was the cause of her suffering.

201
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:08,900
She has been living in my shadow for the past century.

202
00:18:08,900 --> 00:18:12,700
However, she still protected me during that time.

203
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:16,200
  Even so, she shouldn't just frame you like this! 

204
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:20,800
Her kindness and crimes have canceled each other out.

205
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:23,800
Anyway, you shouldn't make it hard on her.

206
00:18:23,800 --> 00:18:29,200
I'm willing to leave this place if Zhi Xi can be relieved of her suffering.

207
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:34,600
Anyway, she's still my sister, no matter what other people say about her.

208
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:36,400
  "Leave this place?" 

209
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:42,500
  Could it be that you're seeking death? 

210
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:44,300
How is that possible?

211
00:18:44,300 --> 00:18:50,700
Emperor Ying Yuan promised he would keep me alive and send me to Mortal Realm.

212
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:54,100
  - Really?   
 - Really!

213
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:55,400
I didn't expect that either.

214
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:57,700
I guess this is a blessing in disguise.

215
00:18:57,700 --> 00:19:00,800
In the past, I used to fantasize about how beautiful the Mortal Realm will be.

216
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:02,300
I wanted to visit it someday.

217
00:19:02,300 --> 00:19:06,000
This time, I guess I can finally check it out myself!

218
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:10,300
  Since you've already decided to go to the Mortal Realm... 

219
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:13,200
 you may never be able to return again. 

220
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:16,300
  Why don't you take Yu Mo with you? 

221
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:19,600
  Emperor Ying Yuan is too far out of your reach. 

222
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:23,800
  So you should consider being with Yu Mo instead. 

223
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:26,600
You like him as a friend, right?

224
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:29,800
Can you not match us up randomly?

225
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:32,600
Yu Mo is the black fish I raised.

226
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:35,100
It's perfectly reasonable even if he regards me as his mother.

227
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:37,000
  I will bear the consequences myself. 

228
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,700
  There's no need to implicate other people. 

229
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:41,500
Anyway, I've already made up my mind.

230
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:43,600
You should stop persuading me.

231
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:49,900
If you can withstand my willfulness and still treat me as a friend,

232
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:54,600
from now on... stand by Emperor Ying Yuan for me.

233
00:19:58,100 --> 00:20:01,600
   

234
00:20:25,100 --> 00:20:27,900
 I do detect the scent of a soul-protecting elixir. 

235
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:18,900
♫   My most bewildering memory is the moonlight falling like frost on the ground full of fallen leaves   ♫

236
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:25,900
♫   For a single teardrop, I'm drowning myself in sorrow, obsessing with forgetting you   ♫

237
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:33,000
♫   If we'd have to walk till we separate, to where would you want to go?   ♫

238
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:39,300
♫   Turn around and become the delusion of my life  ♫

239
00:21:40,100 --> 00:21:47,200
♫   The most beautiful destiny is hidden in the dark night, "love" is the word for everything   ♫

240
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:51,300
♫   My loneliness and longing for you leaves a mark like fragments of the moon   ♫

241
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:57,400
 Your Majesty, I'm an immortal attendant from the Pavilion of Artifacts.  

242
00:21:57,400 --> 00:22:01,400
 I didn't mean to intrude and bother you today. 

243
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:06,500
♫   Life after life, this is the longing I missed the most  ♫

244
