291
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:30,700
 I'll make them for you. 

292
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:32,300
 Sure. 

293
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:51,500
♫   I'll be the oar of a boat and sail into the wind to reach all sides of you   ♫

294
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:54,900
 Come on. Come on! 

295
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:58,300
♫   I'll lean on every ripple to undo the resentments in this lifetime   ♫

296
00:27:58,300 --> 00:28:04,800
♫   A painful apology leads to an inexpressible love I have for you   ♫

297
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:11,600
♫   I don't regret the efforts I put in for us to meet   ♫

298
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:17,400
♫  Following the tracks of the sun and moon, how should I protect you  ♫

299
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:24,500
♫  Again and again, I choose to risk my life  ♫

300
00:28:24,500 --> 00:28:31,600
♫   There are no secrets in the Night Forgetting River, it calls for people to listen   ♫

301
00:28:31,600 --> 00:28:35,400
♫   With a single lantern, all things are settled   ♫

302
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,500
Why were you so foolish?

303
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:46,420
