304
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:50,590
♫   Open one's heart, using the blue sky to embrace the darkness   ♫

305
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:58,000
♫  When you're no longer willing to wait  ♫
♫   No longer willing to love, I'm willing to be your anchor   ♫

306
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:06,000
♫   The gentleness hides the condition of the mortal realm, and you'll be free from doubt   ♫

307
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:11,000
 Although the Butterfly of Lucid Dreams’ cocoon can bring one into the dream realm, 

308
00:29:11,900 --> 00:29:16,700
 only true love can transform the cocoon into a butterfly. 

309
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:22,800
 That night, Yan Dan appeared in my dream. 

310
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:29,100
 The person whom I spent the rest of my life with wasn't just an illusion. 

311
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:33,300
 It was Yan Dan’s real form. 

312
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:41,300
♫   You may choose to hate fate   ♫
♫   Your heart of patience allows me to grieve   ♫

313
00:29:41,300 --> 00:29:51,100
♫   When the fog clears, I will still come carrying my secrets   ♫

314
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:58,600
I've completed the investigation.

315
00:30:58,600 --> 00:31:00,600
You were concocting an elixir...

316
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:05,000
that could protect one's artifact spirit right before you were poisoned.

317
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,800
It would only be effective if you took it three days in a row.

318
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:12,400
You were the one who poisoned yourself.

319
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:18,600
Yan Dan wasn't supposed to be punished.

320
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:23,400
The person who should be sent to the Heavenly Gallows is you.

321
00:31:31,300 --> 00:31:32,800
Yan Dan?

322
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:37,000
Yan Dan.

323
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:42,000
Your Majesty, you only have Yan Dan in your heart.

324
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:50,100
Even though I stood by you for a millennium, why have you never looked at me once?

325
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:58,400
  This is my firefly lamp. It never extinguishes. 

326
00:31:58,400 --> 00:32:02,200
  Emperor Ying Yuan, you're occupied with the affairs of the Heavenly Court every day. You have worked hard. 

327
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:07,500
  I hereby grant you this lamp as a token of appreciation. 

328
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:40,400
  I assume the palace has an abundance of heavenly aura. 

329
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:46,900
  After a millennium, the wick of the firefly lamp actually became an artifact spirit and acquired a human form. 

330
00:33:46,900 --> 00:33:51,100
  Emperor Ying Yuan, she kept you company for a millennium. 

331
00:33:51,100 --> 00:33:55,400
You should take her back and let her serve you in Yanxu Heavenly Palace.

332
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:09,500
Your Majesty and I were fated to be together.

333
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:13,700
Do you really think I don't know?

334
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:22,000
You disrespected the Heavenly Rules and attempted to use a loving relationship to make me enlighten you

335
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:25,700
so that you could transform into an immortal spirit!

336
00:34:25,700 --> 00:34:27,000
That's not it!

337
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:30,000
I admit that I did have an ulterior motive for approaching Your Majesty back then.

338
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:32,400
But I did have feelings for you.

339
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:33,800
You had feelings for me?

340
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:40,589
I was already benevolent enough not to send you to the Heavenly Gallows back then!

341
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,400
Both Yan Dan and I...

342
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:55,400
were your immortal attendants.

343
00:34:56,800 --> 00:35:00,800
I was cautious and loyal to my duties.

344
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:04,200
Not only did she lie, but she also made plenty of mistakes!

345
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:09,200
But Your Majesty defended her and chased me out of the palace instead!

346
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,400
Why?

347
00:35:17,300 --> 00:35:20,800
Your Majesty, why can you never see me?

348
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:28,700
Because immortals should have no feelings.

349
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:33,060
"Immortals should have no feelings"?

350
00:35:33,060 --> 00:35:38,260
If so, Your Majesty, why did you shed tears just now?

351
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:56,440
Your Majesty, if you do have feelings for Yan Dan…

352
00:35:57,340 --> 00:36:00,080
no matter how severe the punishment of love is,

353
00:36:00,080 --> 00:36:06,500
Your Majesty is immensely powerful, and you're protected by His Supreme Majesty. I'm sure you can escape unscathed.

354
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:08,480
But what about Yan Dan?

355
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:14,080
She's still injured and has to face such a severe punishment.

356
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:17,080
I'm afraid she will perish.

357
00:36:24,580 --> 00:36:26,640
Are you trying to threaten me?

358
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:38,320
Your Majesty, I just hope you can spare me.

359
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:40,799
His Supreme Majesty has already given his verdict on the poison.

360
00:36:40,799 --> 00:36:43,659
If you reopen the case again, His Supreme Majesty will surely get to the bottom of it.

361
00:36:43,659 --> 00:36:47,699
The fact that Yan Dan was secretly helping you will be exposed.

362
00:36:47,699 --> 00:36:50,379
His Supreme Majesty has never been lenient toward those who committed the crime of love.

363
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:53,280
If he uses the Uncoupling Cord to test her love for you,

364
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:58,099
I'm afraid she will face the punishment of love, instead of the punishment of fire.

365
00:36:58,099 --> 00:37:01,900
Yan Dan might still survive the punishment of fire.

366
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:06,080
It's better than serving the fatal punishment that is the punishment of love.

367
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:12,440
Your Majesty, if you spare me right now, I will make a vow.

368
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:15,259
I will keep quiet.

369
00:37:15,260 --> 00:37:21,000
I will never tell anyone about your relationship with Yan Dan.

370
00:37:28,220 --> 00:37:33,000
I won't destroy this evidence.

371
00:37:33,780 --> 00:37:39,880
If you dare to do something like this again, I will never spare you.

372
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:43,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

373
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:52,400
I will surely turn over a new leaf. I will never do this again.

374
00:37:52,850 --> 00:37:55,460
You better keep yourself in check from now on.

375
00:38:03,120 --> 00:38:08,080
 Ying Yuan, back then, you rejected me, using the Heavenly Rules as your excuse. 

376
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:14,460
 Now I will watch you as you send the person you love to the Heavenly Gallows. 

377
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:21,000
 She will misunderstand you, hate you, and will never know what you have done for her. 

378
00:38:44,260 --> 00:38:49,759
Emperor Ying Yuan, you told your men to send her belongings here this morning.

379
00:38:49,759 --> 00:38:55,099
Now, although it's getting late, you came all the way to Xuanxin Cliff to clean her room?

380
00:38:57,900 --> 00:39:02,200
Marshal, I have a favor to ask of you.

381
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:04,820
Please help me.

382
00:39:09,790 --> 00:39:10,820
   

383
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:17,940
Back then, I was the one who attacked you.

384
00:39:17,940 --> 00:39:19,659
It's been ages since then.

385
00:39:19,660 --> 00:39:23,959
Moreover, too many things happened in the Heavenly Court during that time.

386
00:39:23,959 --> 00:39:26,340
I've long forgotten about it.

387
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:37,939
You and I were lucky to return from the battlefield alive.

388
00:39:37,939 --> 00:39:42,440
Just tell me if you need any help.

389
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:46,160
Marshal, I hope that you can give me a Letter of Immunity.

390
00:39:46,160 --> 00:39:49,820
A Letter of Immunity? But why?

391
00:39:49,820 --> 00:39:52,900
Could it be that you've committed a grievous sin?

392
00:39:52,900 --> 00:39:57,200
I'm not requesting it for my sake. It's for Yan Dan.

393
00:39:57,200 --> 00:40:00,480
You mean that mischievous brat?

394
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:05,200
She will be punished at the Heavenly Gallows in three days.

395
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:08,880
She has already endured the punishment of thunder strikes.

396
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:13,260
I'm afraid her immortal spirit will perish if she receives the punishment of fire now.

397
00:40:13,260 --> 00:40:18,860
Marshal, that's why I hope you can spare her from punishment with the Letter of Immunity.

398
00:40:18,860 --> 00:40:23,339
What exactly has the little attendant done wrong for her to receive such heavy punishment?

399
00:40:23,339 --> 00:40:26,760
It's inconvenient for me to reveal the reason to you.

400
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:31,320
However, Yan Dan is not a criminal.

401
00:40:36,560 --> 00:40:38,659
You and I have competed for many years.

402
00:40:38,660 --> 00:40:40,419
Your morality can be seen through the way you compete with me.

403
00:40:40,420 --> 00:40:44,019
I know your personality well. I won't ask you why.

404
00:40:44,019 --> 00:40:47,020
I'll do you this favor.

405
00:40:48,620 --> 00:40:52,180
Marshal, I'm deeply indebted to you.

406
00:40:58,020 --> 00:41:01,200
Besides that, I have another favor to ask of you.

407
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:03,600
Speak up.

408
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:08,120
After this, I will transfer Yan Dan back to Xuanxin Cliff.

409
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:11,779
Although she doesn't have much immortal power, she has extraordinary talent.

410
00:41:11,779 --> 00:41:17,640
Marshal, I hope you can take her as your disciple and ensure her future.

411
00:41:18,980 --> 00:41:26,480
Although that little attendant joined hands with you to beat me up, I love sassy brats like her!

412
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:29,559
